@NODE D. "The Dictionary of confused people"

 If you get confused by the odd words in this GUIDE, then look at these..:

@{b}FILE_ID.DIZ@{ub}       = The standard of archieving descriptions inside the actu-
                    al files!

@{b}DIZ@{ub}               = Same as description / File_ID.Diz!

@{b}Desc@{ub}              = WHAT! You dont know this!.. whow... anyway:
                    Shortened form of word: "description"!

@{b}Dizzer@{ub}            = A program that Extracts/Creates automatically a descrip-
                    tion to a file

@{b}SENT-BY@{ub}           = Same as Signature

@{b}Signature@{ub}         = Users "FingerPrint" that will follow every uploaded file
                    as it's own line:

                          ZoolDIZ is the World's BEST describer ever seen!
                          @{b}-----------------------------(-zuulikuuli)----@{ub} <- The SENT-BY


@ENDNODE

