@{b}Known bugs@{ub}................: 

 - None Known... on slow machines ZoolDIZ just won't always work as it should!

 - @{b}These aren't bugs@{ub}...

   1. There are some problems with "Dubbel" - Scan.. For Example..:

   If you upload a archive (ex. with a textfile and 3 sidmodules) and the size
   of the archive is less than 25kbytes, the biggest file will be only proses-
   sed!.. sorry about that, but the possibility, that someone describes a arc-
   hive like this is almost zero! :)  (Mail me if you ran into situation like
   ke this!) [read Dubbel scan at @{"Introduction to the world of ZooLDIZ 2" Link 1.}

   2. In localnode More Prompt appears sometimes, but it's CNets fault... Use
   "full interlaced" screen to prevent this from happening...

